  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras/5dab2f19cfbedbdb61922b90818a68ce.avif?t=1765397946\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras_big/5dab2f19cfbedbdb61922b90818a68ce.avif?t=1765397946 width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras/3ae80d5232985835eb0e925c75d7c3b9.avif?t=1765397946\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras_big/3ae80d5232985835eb0e925c75d7c3b9.avif?t=1765397946 width=800 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras/23315b31e326351385b8fe72fbf97c5e.avif?t=1765397946\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras_big/23315b31e326351385b8fe72fbf97c5e.avif?t=1765397946 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras/3ae80d5232985835eb0e925c75d7c3b9.avif?t=1765397946\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras_big/3ae80d5232985835eb0e925c75d7c3b9.avif?t=1765397946 width=800 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>At the beginning of the year 2153</strong>, the research station \"<strong>Yellow Station</strong>\", located on the edge of the solar system, suddenly stopped responding to all communications from nearby ships and stations.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>The station was completely dead</strong>—there were no signs of life. No signals, not even automatic ones, were being transmitted. </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>The silence was absolute...</strong></i><strong> <br> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras/3ae80d5232985835eb0e925c75d7c3b9.avif?t=1765397946\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras_big/3ae80d5232985835eb0e925c75d7c3b9.avif?t=1765397946 width=800 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras/2d1e82de8c02a7b3f4cf77654cc64921.avif?t=1765397946\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras_big/2d1e82de8c02a7b3f4cf77654cc64921.avif?t=1765397946 width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras/3ae80d5232985835eb0e925c75d7c3b9.avif?t=1765397946\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras_big/3ae80d5232985835eb0e925c75d7c3b9.avif?t=1765397946 width=800 height=59 /></span><strong><br>Hollow Space</strong> is an immersive multiplayer game that transports players to a mysterious, abandoned space station where tension and adrenaline reach their peak. By stepping into the shoes of a special crew member or a mutant, you face dangerous challenges that will determine the fate of the station.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>As a crew member</strong>, your main objective is to eliminate mutants and regain control of the station. Utilize your skills, strategy, and available resources to solve the station's puzzles, find hidden items, and avoid the dangers lurking at every turn. The game requires cooperation with other crew members to effectively confront mutant foes, whose combat abilities can surprise even the most skilled players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras/3ae80d5232985835eb0e925c75d7c3b9.avif?t=1765397946\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras_big/3ae80d5232985835eb0e925c75d7c3b9.avif?t=1765397946 width=800 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                        <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras/18d829fe9019147b0dba1bc16330828b.poster.avif?t=1765397946\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras/18d829fe9019147b0dba1bc16330828b.webm?t=1765397946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras/18d829fe9019147b0dba1bc16330828b.mp4?t=1765397946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras/3ae80d5232985835eb0e925c75d7c3b9.avif?t=1765397946\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras_big/3ae80d5232985835eb0e925c75d7c3b9.avif?t=1765397946 width=800 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>As a mutant</strong>, you must leverage your strength, agility, and intelligence to face off against the crew. Your mission is to fight the crew members and sabotage their plans while uncovering the station's secrets and gaining the upper hand. As a mutant, you have access to unique abilities that allow you to catch opponents off guard and create chaos in their ranks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras/3ae80d5232985835eb0e925c75d7c3b9.avif?t=1765397946\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras_big/3ae80d5232985835eb0e925c75d7c3b9.avif?t=1765397946 width=800 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras/f04a24a3ce59bbb7b94a24b9bf7e88ee.poster.avif?t=1765397946\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras/f04a24a3ce59bbb7b94a24b9bf7e88ee.webm?t=1765397946\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras/f04a24a3ce59bbb7b94a24b9bf7e88ee.mp4?t=1765397946\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras/3ae80d5232985835eb0e925c75d7c3b9.avif?t=1765397946\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3325840/extras_big/3ae80d5232985835eb0e925c75d7c3b9.avif?t=1765397946 width=800 height=59 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
